_sText:
I really liked the Nipper house, a cool map that went very well with the simple nightcrawler mod I made to play with bots and online.

The two decorative side houses were missing, not being able to enter them really was missed, so I decided to draw them on the inside to improve the gameplay.

This map modification has 3 bombsites, and I also made another version of this same map, but this one is for hostage rescue with random spawn.
